%F A394103 Equals (3/4)^(1/3) * (4/105 + 13*sqrt(2)/105 - 4*Pi/45 + 109*log(3)/(630*sqrt(2)) + 16*arccot(sqrt(2))/315 + 158*arccoth(sqrt(2))*sqrt(2)/315).
